There's a variety of tutorials about Pokémon SDK. Here's a list:

- **How to start a fangame:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hkxUMJ5okrQ)
- **How to create/modify a Pokémon:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PhubKm74tTk)
- **How to create/modify a move:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/KCrTp-AWlg4)
- **How to create/modify an item:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/ZcnTKIjrweo)
- **How to create/modify a type:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/SGzRidoGN5M)
- **How to create/modify a Pokédex:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/je9W-5tWh-Q)
- **How to create/modify a zone:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/Dm0c7u5oPhw)
- **How to create/modify wild Pokémon:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/Dm0c7u5oPhw?t=372)
- **How to create/modify a Trainer:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/Rzr5qAghB_g)
- **How to upload your project to Git:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/Fv87nZt9gwg)
- **How to create a monkeypatch:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/CQphy2qzfV0)
- **How to create an ability:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/aLDgRrLccQs)
- **How to create/modify a Trainer:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/Rzr5qAghB_g)
- **How to map with Tiled:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/5A8gjBRGAAI)
- **How to create a region map:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/8aitmraK2UY)
- **How to create a new options:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/IZlpDx873IA)
- **How to create a plugin:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/Xi7V0mj3_Fw)
- **How to contribute to PSDK:** [Video tutorial on Youtube](https://youtu.be/tq3ETmnqzWQ)
- **Event making with RMXP & PSDK:** [Event Making in RMXP](/en/help/event-making-in-rmxp)
- **Handling errors in PSDK:** [How to handle errors](/en/help/pokemon-sdk/my-game-crashs-and-i-don-t-know-what-to-do)
- **How to add scripts:** [Old video tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BSb3YwxnvIQ) (not compatible with non-git project), [Baguette video tutorial](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E9zYkR_3rbM)
- **How to introduce your project** : [Create a project page](/en/help/website/create-a-project-page)

